### **Installing and loading the packages**



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
pacman::p_load(haven, SmartEDA, tidyverse, tidymodels)
```
:::



### **Data import**



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
exam_data <- read.csv("Exam_data.csv")
```
:::



### Plotting boxplot



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data = exam_data,
       aes(x = ENGLISH,
           y = CLASS)) +
  geom_boxplot()
```
